'''縮陽症'''（英語：koro）或稱'''恐縮症'''，是一種常見於[[中國|中國]]和[[東南亞|東南亞]]地區的[[文化結合症候群|文化結合症候群]]（Culture-bound syndrome）及[[心理疾病|心理疾病]]，患者即使其[[生殖器官|生殖器官]]沒有任何真正的變化<ref>{{cite web|title=Koro|url=http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/koro|publisher=dictionary.com|accessdate=April 1, 2013}}</ref>，仍會堅稱他的[[生殖器官|生殖器官]]正在縮入體內，並且堅信其完全縮進人體就會致死<ref>Eng-Seong Tam:海外華人的文化心理症狀。林宗義、Arthur Kleinman編、柯永河、蕭欣義譯：文化與行為—古今華人的正常與不正常行為。香港：中文大學出版，1990; 315-326</ref>，它被[[精神疾病診斷與統計手冊|精神疾病診斷與統計手冊]]所收錄。此病全球都有發生記錄，在[[非洲|非洲]]，[[亞洲|亞洲]]和[[歐洲|歐洲]]，與[[生殖器官|生殖器官]]收縮恐慌相關的[[集體歇斯底里|集體歇斯底里]]有一定歷史。<ref name="MattelaerJilek2007">{{cite journal|last1=Mattelaer|first1=Johan J.|last2=Jilek|first2=Wolfgang|title=Koro?The Psychological Disappearance of the Penis|journal=The Journal of Sexual Medicine|volume=4|issue=5|year=2007|pages=1509–1515|issn=1743-6095|doi=10.1111/j.1743-6109.2007.00586.x}}</ref>在[[美國|美國]]和[[歐洲|歐洲]]，此症通常稱為生殖器后缩綜合症（genital retraction syndrome）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://science.discovery.com/top-ten/2009/mental-disorders/mental-disorders-5.html |title=Top 10 Little-Known Mental Disorders |publisher=Discovery Communications |accessdate=15 July 2012}}</ref>。可通過心理評估以及[[身體檢查|身體檢查]]，排除其他可能導致[[生殖器官|生殖器官]]縮入體內的疾病<ref name="ReferenceA">Chowdhury AN. The definition and classification of koro. Cult Med Psychiatry 1996;20:41–65.</ref><ref name="Ghanem, H. 2012">Ghanem, H., Glina, S., Assalian, P., & Buvat, J.（2012）. Position Paper: Management of Men Complaining of a Small Penis Despite an Actually Normal Size. The Journal of Sexual Medicine.</ref>。

==類別==
在[[DSM-IV-TR|DSM-IV-TR]]，縮陽症被收錄在附件一[[文化結合症候群|文化結合症候群]]的列表中，把它定義為「一個可能源於[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]的術語，指突然和劇烈的焦慮，對[[陰莖|陰莖]]（或女性的[[女陰|女陰]]或[[乳房|乳房]]）會縮入人體这点感到恐懼，患者堅信這樣甚至可能導致死亡」<ref name = "DSM-IV-TR">{{cite book | last = American Psychiatric Association | title = Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders, 4th ed., text revision | publisher = American Psychiatric Pub | year = 2000 | pages = 898–901 | isbn = 978-0-89042-025-6}}</ref>。

不同的研究員也曾嘗試把縮陽症分類，例如縮陽症可能符合「特定文化下的疑病障礙」（specific culture-imposed nosophobia，以主要症狀分類）<ref>{{Citation | last = Yap | first = Pow-Meng | title = Classification of the Culture-Bound Reactive Syndromes | journal = Australian and New Zealand Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 1 | issue = 4 | pages = 172–9 | year = 1967 | issn = 0004-8674 | doi=10.3109/00048676709159191}}</ref>、「因與文化有關的的信念而發生」（culture-related beliefs as causes for the occurrence，以文化的影響為主要考慮因素）。

研究者也試圖把縮陽症以按着或不按着文化形態完整或不完整地區分<ref name = "Adeniran 1994">{{Citation | last = Adeniran | first = R. A. | last2 = Jones | first2 = J. R. | title = Koro: Culture-Bound Disorder or Universal Symptom?| journal = British Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 164 | issue = 4 | pages = 559–61 | date = April 1994 | issn = 0007-1250 | doi=10.1192/bjp.164.4.559}}</ref>。縮陽症的「傳播」被認為是[[文化|文化]][[信仰|信仰]]和[[神話|神話]]所起的作用，且已有一套完善的診斷標準。<ref name = "Adeniran 1994"/><ref name="auto">{{Citation | last = Chowdhury | first = Arabinda N. | title = The definition and classification of Koro | journal = Culture, Medicine & Psychiatry | volume = 20 | issue = 1| pages = 41–65 | date = March 1996 | issn = 0165-005X | doi=10.1007/bf00118750}}</ref>縮陽症可分為原發性和繼發性兩類：原發性縮陽症是與文化信念密切的心理障礙；繼發性縮陽症是以[[中樞神經系統|中樞神經系統]]病變、懼患其他[[精神病|精神病]]，或使用[[藥物|藥物]]為基礎上所產生<ref name = "Chowdhury 1996"/>。[[中醫|中醫]]則認為縮陽症是一種性功能障礙，為腎陽虧損、寒阻肝經所致<ref>{{Citation | last = Wang | first = Minghui | last2 = Wang | first2 = Fenglei | title = Conceptualisation and treatment of koro in traditional Chinese medicine | journal = The Chinese Journal of Human Sexuality | volume = 11 | issue = 1 | pages = 559–61 | date = March 2002 | language = zh | issn = 1672-1993}}</ref>。

== 詞源和地理背景 ==
[[西方|西方]]最早使用"koro"的據典為1874年的《布吉语词典》（B.F. Matthes' Dictionary of Buginese Language (1874) of South Sulawesi, Indonesia）<ref name = "Chowdhury 1998">{{Citation | last = Chowdhury | first = Arabinda N. | title = Hundred Years of Koro: The History of a Culture-Bound Syndrome | journal = The International Journal of Social Psychiatry | volume = 44 |issue = 3| pages = 181–8 | date = September 1998 | issn = 0020-7640 | doi=10.1177/002076409804400304}}</ref>，名稱可能來自一條[[河流|河流]]、其周圍的[[山谷|山谷]]、[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]的[[蘇拉威西島|蘇拉威西島]]西北部的一個地方部落<ref name=thedisordernamedkoro>{{cite journal|last1=Durst|first1=Rimona|title=The Disorder Named Koro|journal=Behavioural Neurology|date=1991|volume=4|issue=1|pages=1–14|doi=10.3233/BEN-1991-4101|pmid=24487349|url=http://downloads.hindawi.com/journals/bn/1991/525393.pdf|accessdate=3 June 2015}}</ref>。也是[[望加錫|望加錫語]]的一個單詞，意指「收縮」；完整的表達為「garring koro」<ref name="auto"/><ref name = "Chowdhury 1996">{{Citation | last = Chowdhury | first = Arabinda N. | title = The definition and classification of Koro | journal = Culture, Medicine & Psychiatry | volume = 20 | issue = 1| pages = 41–65 | date = March 1996 | issn = 0165-005X | doi=10.1007/bf00118750}}</ref>。也可能來自[[馬來語|馬來語]]「Kura」，意指「龜的頭部」<ref name=thedisordernamedkoro/><ref name = "Cheng 1996">{{Citation | last = Cheng | first = Sheung-Tak | title = A Critical Review of Chinese Koro | journal = Culture, Medicine & Psychiatry | volume = 20 | issue = 1| pages = 41–65 | date = March 1996 |issn = 0165-005X}}</ref>或馬來語的「keruk」，也指「收縮」。<ref>{{Citation | last = Palthe | first = W. P. M. van | title = Koro, een Eigenaardige Angstneurose | journal = Geneeskundig Tijdschrift voor Nederlandsch-Indie | volume = 74 | pages = 1713–1720 | year = 1934}}</ref>縮陽症也被稱為「rok loo」（[[泰國|泰國]]）、「jinjinnia bemar」（[[阿薩姆|阿薩姆]]和[[印度|印度]]）、「lanuk e laso」（[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]巴格博部落）<ref name=thedisordernamedkoro/>

== 流行病學 ==
這種對[[生殖器官|生殖器官]]縮入人體的[[恐懼|恐懼]]或[[焦慮|焦慮]]的症病在[[中國|中國]]、[[印度|印度]]、[[日本|日本]]為最普遍，在[[中國|中國]]，縮陽症的病發僅限於[[南中國|南中國]]和[[長江下游|長江下游]]。<ref name = "Yap 1965"/>一份1992年的問卷調查發現中國的縮陽症患者大多為[[漢族|漢族]]、[[男性|男性]]、年紀較為年輕、單身、教育程度低、對超自然力量和縮陽症有所恐懼。<ref name = "Cheng 1996"/>這種現象除了在中國擁有之外，也在許多[[東南亞國家|東南亞國家]]發現，尤其是[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]和[[印尼|印尼]]，[[馬來|馬來]]和[[印尼|印尼]]居民則相對較少發生。<ref name = "Yap 1965"/>雖然有人猜測縮陽症在[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]和[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]發生是中國移民所帶來的後果，但因為在[[泰國|泰國]]和印度中也已有由非中國人傳播的病例，因此縮陽症在某些地區傳播是「中國移民的後果」的觀點備受挑戰。<ref name = "Tseng 2006">{{Citation | last = Tseng | first = W. S. | title = From Peculiar Psychiatric Disorders through Culture-bound Syndromes to Culture-related Specific Syndromes | journal = Transcultural Psychiatry | volume = 43 | issue = 4 | pages = 554–576 | date = December 2006 | doi=10.1177/1363461506070781}}</ref>

縮陽症的零星病例亦在非東南亞人種身上發生，如[[尼泊爾人|尼泊爾人]]<ref>{{Citation | last = Chowdhury | first = A. N. | last2 =  Rajbhandari | first2 = K. C. | title = Koro with Depression in Nepal | journal = Transcultural Psychiatric Research Review | volume = 32 | pages = 87–90 | year = 1994 | doi=10.1177/136346159503200108}}</ref>、[[蘇丹|蘇丹人]]<ref>{{Citation | last = Baasher | first = T. A. | title = The Influence of Culture on Psychiatric Manifestation | journal = Transcultural Psychiatric Research Review | volume = 15 | pages = 51–2 | year = 1963}}</ref>、[[約旦|約旦人]]<ref>{{Citation | last = Al-Hmoud| first = N. | title = Koro-like syndrome in a Jordanian male | journal = Eastern Mediterranean Health Journal | volume = 5 | issue = 3 | pages = 611–3 | year = 1999}}</ref>、[[坦桑尼亞|坦桑尼亞人]]<ref>{{Citation | last = Lucieer| first = W. M. | title = The Bitter Taste of Liberty: A Study in Ethnopsychiatry | journal = Psychopathologic Africane | volume = 20 | pages = 17–40 | year = 1984}}</ref>、[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞人]]<ref>{{Citation | last = Ifabumunyi | first = O. I. | last2 = Rwegellera | first2 = G. G. C. | title = Koro in a Nigerian Male Patient: A Case Report| journal = African Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 5 | pages = 103–5 | year = 1979}}</ref>、[[法國人|法國人]]<ref>{{Citation | last = Burgeois | first = M. | title = Un Koro Charentais (Transposition Ethnopsychiatrique) | journal = Annales Medico Psychologiques | volume = 126 | pages = 749–51 | year = 1896}}</ref>、[[英國人|英國人]]<ref>{{Citation | last = Barrett| first = K. | title = Koro in a Londoner | journal = The Lancet | volume = 8103 | issue = 2 | pages = 1319 | year = 1978 | doi=10.1016/s0140-6736（78）92093-7}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | last = Yap | first = Pow-Meng | title = Koro in a Briton | journal = British Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 111 | issue = 477 | pages = 774–5 | date = August 1965 | issn = 0007-1250 | doi=10.1192/bjp.111.477.774-a}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | last = Cremona | first = Anne | title = Another case of koro in a Briton | journal = British Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 138 | issue = 2 | pages = 180–1 | date = February 1981 | issn = 0007-1250 | doi=10.1192/bjp.138.2.180}}</ref>、[[美國人|美國人]]<ref>{{Citation | last = Bychowski | first = G. | title = Psychotherapy of Psychosis| pages = 109–10 | publisher = Grune and Stratton | location = New York | year = 1952}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | last = Edwards | first = J. G. | title = The Koro pattern of depersonalization in an American schizophrenic patient | journal = American Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 126 | pages = 1171–3 | year = 1970 | doi=10.1176/ajp.126.8.1171}}</ref>、[[加拿大人|加拿大人]]<ref>{{Citation | last = Dow | first = T. W. | last2 = Silver | first2 = D. | title = A drug induced Koro syndrome | journal = Journal of Florida Medical Association | volume = 60 | pages = 32–3 | year = 1973}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | last = Ede| first = A. | title = Koro in an Anglo-Saxon Canadian | journal = Canadian Psychiatric Association Journal | volume = 21 | pages = 389–92 | year = 1976}}</ref>等國家人民都有病例。在大多數[[西半球|西半球]]非中國患者的情況下，不會出現縮陽症的典型症狀，如對死亡的恐懼。<ref>{{Citation | last = Kumar | first = H. V. | title = Koro in an Israeli Man| journal = British Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 150 | issue = 1 | pages = 133b | date = January 1987 | issn = 0007-1250 | doi=10.1192/bjp.150.1.133b}}</ref>非典型縮陽症的会被稱為非文化樣式（non-cultural forms），而伴有急性焦慮的完整樣式（the complete form with acute anxiety）則是典型的文化束縛型。

== 症狀 ==
大多數患者即使其生殖器沒有任何客觀可見的長期變化，也會報稱因自感[[生殖器|生殖器]]縮入體內而驚恐發作，「長期」是指明顯且不可逆的持續變化，不像低溫令生殖器縮小般的正常影響。雖然寒冷氣溫的影響是客觀可逆的，但當「準患者」觀察到低溫令生殖器縮小这一正常現象时可能會誘發縮陽症。<ref>{{Citation | last = Ngui | first = P. W. | title = The Koro Epidemic in Singapore | journal = Australian and New Zealand Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 3 | issue = 3a（special issue on studies of anxiety） | pages = 263–6 | year = 1969 | issn = 0004-8674}}</ref>據文獻所記載，縮陽症的發作时長通常为幾個小時，極端情況下甚至長達兩天。<ref name = "Yap 1965">{{Citation | last = Yap | first = Pow-Meng | title = Koro—A Culture-Bound Depersonalization Syndrome | journal = British Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 111 | pages = 45–50 | year = 1965 | issn = 0007-1250 | doi = 10.1192/bjp.111.470.43}}</ref>另外還有一些例子，縮陽症症狀持續多年的情況下，會有伴發[[身體畸形恐懼症|身體畸形恐懼症]]的風險<ref name = "Chowdhury 1996"/><ref name="dsm5.org">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dsm5.org/research/documents/phillips_bdd.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-02-09 |archive-date=2010-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100705184318/http://www.dsm5.org/research/documents/phillips_bdd.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了自感[[生殖器|生殖器]]收縮外，其他症狀还包括患者抱有「陰莖的形狀改變」和「陰莖肌肉的張力喪失」之类的看法。在某些情況下，患者可能沒有[[生殖器|生殖器]]收縮的感覺，但會抱怨「外陰感覺異常」或「生殖器縮短了」。<ref>{{Citation | last = Chowdhury | first = Arabinda N. | title = Clinical Analysis of 101 Koro Cases | journal = Indian Journal of Social Psychiatry | volume = 8 | pages = 67–70 | year = 1992}}</ref>在女性患者中，主要症狀是自感[[乳頭|乳頭]]向內縮入[[乳房|乳房]]或乳房縮入體內<ref>曹興午，[http://blog.sina.com.tw/45741/article.php?pbgid=45741&entryid=577044 縮陽症是一種不良文化背景的恐懼症]，華人性健康報第五期，2008</ref>，與身體成為一體<ref name = "Chowdhury 1996"/>

心理症狀包括恐懼[[死亡|死亡]]即將到來、陰莖的消失及喪失性能力<ref name = "Chowdhury 1996"/><ref>Mattelaer, J. and Jilek, W.（2007, September）. Koro—The psychological disappearance of the penis. Retrieved March 5, 2013 from Ebscohost Database.[http://huie.hsu.edu:2308/ehost/detail?vid=3&sid=0d3bfe6e-d98c-4a3c-80dd-d0f697cf6987%40sessionmgr4&hid=2&bdata=JnNpdGU9ZWhvc3QtbGl2ZQ%3d%3d#db=psyh&AN=2007-12836-027]{{Dead link|date=2019年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>並在發作時有強烈的瀕死感，與大多數西方的患者不同，亞洲的患者普遍認為縮陽症是致命的<ref name = "Chowdhury 1996"/><ref name = "Cheng 1996"/>，其他心理症狀包括擔心內臟萎縮，害怕變為[[女性|女性]]或[[太監|太監]]，擔憂自身安全，自感尿路梗阻，害怕將因此而導致[[不育|不育]]，覺得即將瘋掉，精神被人或[[鬼魂|鬼魂]]侵佔和被迷惑的感覺。<ref name = "Chowdhury 1996"/>

男性患者和他們的家人可能會採取物理上的方法，以防止陰莖縮入體內，患者可能以夹具拉扯或固定陰莖達到其目的（防止陰莖縮入體內）<ref name = "Gwee 1963">{{Citation | last = Gwee | first = Ah Leng | title = Koro—A Cultural Disease | journal = Singapore Medical Journal | volume = 4 | pages = 119–22 | year = 1963}}</ref>。同樣，女性患者可能會抓住自己的乳房、拉住她的乳頭，甚至以鐵針插入乳頭「固定」它<ref name = "Cheng 1996"/>。這些「救治方法」往往會導致患者受傷，甚至死亡。<ref>{{Citation | last = Garlipp | first = Petra | title = Koro – a Culture-Bound Phenomenon Intercultural Psychiatric Implications | journal = German Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 11  | pages = 21–8 | year = 2008 | issn = 1433-1055}}</ref>

== 病因 ==
性心理因素、人格因素和文化信仰被認為是縮陽症的主要病因<ref name = "Adeniran 1994"/>。非中國籍患者的性調整史往往較顯著，如發病前[[性交|性交]]不足、性濫交、對[[自慰|自慰]]有強烈的內疚感，以及患上[[勃起功能障礙|勃起功能障礙]]。<ref>{{Citation | last = Berrios | first = G. E. | last2 = Morley | first2 = S. | title = Koro-like Symptoms in Non-Chinese Subjects | journal = British Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 145 | issue = 3 | pages = 331–4 | date = September 1984 | issn = 0007-1250 | doi=10.1192/bjp.145.3.331}}</ref>

===演化和生物學觀點===
當考慮到生物學機制與縮陽症的演化史之間的关系，最重要的是聚焦於它在群眾歇斯底里的架構。儘管發病機制仍然知之甚少，[[鏡像神經元|鏡像神經元]]已被認為在集體歇斯底里的爆發中起了一個重要作用。鏡像神經元發現於人類和非人靈長類動物的身體中，用以模仿被觀察到的行為。有一個这樣的假設：人类演化出這些機制從觀察他人來學習以及便於模仿，不過，鏡像神經元中有某種抑制過程，這使得人类無法盲目模仿每次所觀察到的行為。有研究表明，集體歇斯底里爆發時此抑制過程出現了異常<ref>Lee, Yao-Tung and Tsai, Shih-Jen, The mirror neuron system may play a role in the pathogenesis of mass hysteria, ''Medical Hypotheses'' 2010, p 244</ref>

== 體檢 ==
一個完整的醫療、心理和精神病史應被記錄。醫師應探討病人的有關外觀和身體形象（排除軀體變形障礙）的擔憂。此外，醫師亦應詢問患者的整體信念、個人[[價值觀|價值觀]]和患者對他或她的生殖器的臆測。鑑於縮陽症通常是一種與「攻擊」有極大關聯的焦慮，所以醫師應以時間軸記錄從發病到診斷期間病人的情緒狀態。<ref>Berrios GE, Morley SJ. Koro-like symptom in a non-Chinese subject. ''Br J Psychiatry'' 1984;145: 331–4.</ref><ref name="Wylie, K. R. 2007">Wylie, K. R., & Eardley, I.（2007）. Penile size and the ‘small penis syndrome’.BJU international, 99（6）, 1449-1455.</ref><ref>Jilek WG, Jilek-Aall L. A koro epidemic in Thailand. Transcult Psychiatr Res Rev 1977;14:57–9.</ref>體檢應包括評估病人的整體健康狀況，詳細地檢查其生殖器。對於男性患者的體檢，應在陰莖曝露於外後立即進行檢查，以避免陰莖的大小受到外部溫度的影響，而令檢查結果更準確。男性體檢的主要目的是排除生理病變，如[[尿道下裂|尿道下裂]]、尿道上裂，以及陰莖硬結症<ref name="ReferenceA"/><ref name="Wylie, K. R. 2007"/>。[[恥骨|恥骨]]上脂肪墊的存在也應注意<ref name="Elder JS PC">Elder JS. Congenital anomalies of the genitalia. In:Walsh PC,Retik AB, Walsh PC, Campbell MF, eds. Campell’s urology. Philadelphia, London, Toronto: W.B. Saunders Comp.; 1998: 2120–43.</ref>。仔細測量陰莖疲軟時及勃起时的長度，以及周長也是對体檢有幫助的。如果男性患者堅持認為自己的陰莖正在縮入體內及即將消失<ref name="ReferenceA"/>，可在[[前列腺素E1|前列地爾]]注射到陰莖[[海綿體|海綿體]]後進行測量，以確定真正的勃起長度，並在勃起狀態診斷任何與陰莖有關的生理異常<ref name="Wylie, K. R. 2007"/>。體檢時應注意因患者盡力「防止」生殖器縮入體內而造成的任何傷害，可作為診斷的參考依據<ref name="ReferenceA"/>。

== 診斷 ==
幾個診斷標準常被用於縮陽症的診斷。主要的診斷標準是即使缺乏客觀的證據證明，患者仍會自感生殖器（通常為陰莖或女性乳頭）縮入體內，常伴隨著與縮阳有關的嚴重焦慮，恐懼縮陽會令自身死亡，和使用工具以防止生殖器縮入體內<ref name = "Dzokkoto 2005">{{Citation | last = Dzokkoto | first = Vivian Afi | last2 = Adams | first2 = Glenn | title = Understanding genital-shrinking epidemics in West Africa : koro, juju or mass psychogenic illness? | journal = Culture, Medicine and Psychiatry | volume = 29 | issue = 3 | pages = 53–78 | year = 2005 | issn = 0165-005X | doi=10.1007/s11013-005-4623-8}}</ref>。若不符合所有診斷標準，就會被診斷為“類縮陽症”（koro-like symptoms）或“部分縮陽症”（partial koro syndrome）<ref name = "Dzokkoto 2005"/>。研究人員已經確定縮陽症可能是一种“文化相對性”的[[軀體變形障礙|軀體變形障礙]]，因此[[DSM-IV|DSM-IV]]解釋了這兩種疾病的鑑別診斷的方法<ref name="dsm5.org"/>。
